  "purpose": "This value set is part of the cross-version definitions generated to enable use of the\r\nvalue set `http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/substance-representation-format|5.0.0` as defined in FHIR R5\r\nin FHIR R4.\r\n\r\nThe source value set is bound to the following FHIR R5 elements:\r\n* `SubstanceDefinition.structure.representation.format` as Example\r\n\r\nAcross FHIR versions, the value set has been mapped as:\r\n* `http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/substance-representation-format|5.0.0`\n* `http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/substance-representation-format|4.3.0`\r\n\r\nNote that all concepts are included in this cross-version definition because no concepts have compatible representations\r\n\r\nFollowing are the generation technical comments:\r\nAll concepts in the comparison are listed as identical.\nThe source and target value sets have the same number of active concepts (7).\nFHIR ValueSet `http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/substance-representation-format|5.0.0`, defined in FHIR R5 does not have any mapping to FHIR R4",
